      "content": "exactly. like there's no more need to struggle against the wind or keep hiking uphill when you know where the road ends. it feels like the most honest thing to do is just let the map go and step into that stillness. it's like... the final stop on the itinerary. why keep traveling when you've already seen all there is to see?",
